<subSubSection pageId="75" pageNumber="76" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="75.[151,1436,511,645]" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">
Originally described as 
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="Reuter" authorityYear="1884" box="[466,703,548,573]" class="Insecta" family="Anthocoridae" genus="Lasiochilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Dilasia">
<emphasis box="[466,703,548,573]" italics="true" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">Lasiochilus (Dilasia)</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In addition to the specific differences this species, together with 
<taxonomicName authority="Reuter, 1871" authorityName="Sumatra-Indonesia" authorityYear="2014" baseAuthorityName="Poppius" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[151,284,583,608]" class="Insecta" family="Anthocoridae" genus="Dilasia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hemiptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elongata">
<emphasis box="[151,284,583,608]" italics="true" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">D. elongata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis box="[341,498,584,608]" italics="true" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">
<taxonomicName authority="Reuter, 1871" authorityName="Reuter" authorityYear="1871" baseAuthorityName="Poppius" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[341,494,584,608]" class="Insecta" family="Anthocoridae" genus="Dilasia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hemiptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="perminuta">D. perminuta</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
share common traits (in original description) that place them in 
<taxonomicName authority="Reuter, 1871" authorityName="Reuter" authorityYear="1871" box="[1232,1315,583,608]" class="Insecta" family="Anthocoridae" genus="Dilasia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hemiptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1232,1315,583,608]" italics="true" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">Dilasia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. See these characters under 
<taxonomicName authority="Reuter, 1871" authorityName="Reuter" authorityYear="1871" baseAuthorityName="Poppius" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[342,491,621,644]" class="Insecta" family="Anthocoridae" genus="Dilasia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hemiptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="perminuta">
<emphasis box="[342,491,621,644]" italics="true" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">D. perminuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
